data.description: Property back on the market, offering a fresh opportunity for interested parties. Contact for details." Are you looking for the perfect balance of comfort and energy efficiency? Look no further than this delightful single-family home in the heart of Deltona. This well-maintained property is full of potential, with numerous recent upgrades that make it an attractive and cost-effective choice. Enjoy the benefits of living with a solar panel lease that can help you save on energy bills. Stay cool and comfortable year-round with a brand-new air conditioning system, ensuring you're always at the perfect temperature. The roof, a critical home component, has been recently replaced, offering peace of mind, a new water heater, and a garage door opener. This home, built in 2006, offers modern construction and is ready for your personal touch and updates. While the exterior has been well taken care of, the home interior presents a blank canvas for your creative ideas and personalization. You can transform it into your dream space, reflecting your style and taste. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a showing, and explore the potential of this wonderful property.
